        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🎵 POLKA</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">11 pts · P=3, O=1, L=1, K=5, A=1 · Czech dance</p></div>
